entropypianotuner (1.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Disabled all context menus on the tool bars (Closes: #32)
  * Removed assertions on unlikely data (Closes: #37, #38, #40)
  * Usage of QtMidi for midi support (Closes: #30)
  * Algortihms as library plugin (Closes: #21)
  * Reworked audio backend (Closes: #34)
  * EPT files always written as UTF-8 (Closes: #37)
  * Loading audio devices in separate thread (Closes: #33)
  * Bug fixes (Closes: #26, #31, #35, #36, #44, #45)
  * Implementing improvements (Closes: #41)

 -- Christoph Wick <info@piano-tuner.org>  Mon, 20 Feb 2017 21:20:41 +0100

